      <title>据《华尔街日报》报道，苹果与中国百度就其设备的人工智能进行了谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-held-talks-with-chinas-baidu-over-ai-use-its-devices-wsj-reports-2024-03-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《华尔街日报》周五报道，苹果已与百度 9888.HK 就在其中国设备中使用这家中国公司的生成式人工智能技术进行了初步谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-held-talks-with-chinas-baidu-over-ai-use-its-devices-wsj-reports-2024-03-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 12:30:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>州长称菲律宾将在台湾附近建设新岛屿港口，无需美国帮助</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-build-new-islands-port-near-taiwan-without-us-help-governor-says-2024-03-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当地州长周五表示，美国军方不会参与台湾附近菲律宾最北端偏远岛屿的港口开发，从而消除了因美国在该地区存在而与中国发生摩擦的潜在根源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-build-new-islands-port-near-taiwan-without-us-help-governor-says-2024-03-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 12:13:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
