      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/rupee-hits-record-low-posts-steepest-weekly-fall-seven-months-2024-03-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员表示，周五印度卢比兑美元汇率跌至历史新低，受到离岸人民币贬值和接近尾盘时强劲的当地美元需求的压力。]]></description>
